      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "PERSONAL TRAINER\n\nBetween sessions. Gym floor.\nSweat on the screen. One thumb.\n\"Approve the €80 class-pack? Now?\nOr ask me in 10?\"",
