      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "CONTEXT, NOT CLUTTER\n\nThe owner sees exactly what\nthey need — action, customer,\nhistory, risk — and nothing more.\n\nSometimes that's a lot.\nSometimes it's almost nothing.\nKnowing the difference is the\ncraft.",
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CONTEXT, NOT CLUTTER\n\nThe owner sees exactly what\nthey need — action, customer,\nhistory, risk — and nothing more.\n\nSometimes that's a lot.\nSometimes it's almost nothing.\nKnowing the difference is the\ncraft.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14
    },
