      "roundness": null, "seed": 621, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 621,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "THE CUSTOMER SIDE\n\nWhat does the customer see\nwhile the owner decides?\n\nSilence is a design choice.\nSo is \"let me double-check\nfor you.\"\n\nDon't leave them hanging.",
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "THE CUSTOMER SIDE\n\nWhat does the customer see\nwhile the owner decides?\n\nSilence is a design choice.\nSo is \"let me double-check\nfor you.\"\n\nDon't leave them hanging.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14
    },
