      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "THE HANDOFF BACK\n\nOnce the owner decides —\nhow does the agent continue?\n\nConfidently. In-character.\nWithout breaking the\nconversation.\n\nThe seam should be invisible.",
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "THE HANDOFF BACK\n\nOnce the owner decides —\nhow does the agent continue?\n\nConfidently. In-character.\nWithout breaking the\nconversation.\n\nThe seam should be invisible.",
